START
Ask the user to enter number 1 
Ask the user to enter number 2
Read number 1,2
Ask the user for operators + or -
Read operator
Perform calculation based on the operator
IF the operator is +
Answer =number 1 + number 2
ELSE the operator is -
Answer =number 1 - number 2
ELSE PRINT "operator is invalid,use operator + or -"
